 -- Function: kurtosis_geometric (P)
     Returns the kurtosis coefficient of a geometric random variable
     {\it Geometric}(p) , with 0 < p \leq 1.

     The kurtosis coefficient is

     KU[X] = {p^2-6p+6 \over 1-p}

