     ‘load("distrib")’ loads this function.


File: maxima-core-docs.info,  Node: Function kurtosis_gumbel a b,  Next: Function kurtosis_hypergeometric n_1 n_2 n,  Prev: Function kurtosis_geometric p,  Up: distrib

 -- Function: kurtosis_gumbel (A, B)
     Returns the kurtosis coefficient of a {\it Gumbel}(a,b) random
     variable, with b>0.  To make use of this function, write first
     ‘load("distrib")’.

     The kurtosis coefficient is

     KU[X] = {12\over 5}

