 -- Function: quantile_student_t (Q, N)
     Returns the _q_-quantile of a Student random variable t(n) , with
     n>0; in other words, this is the inverse of ‘cdf_student_t’.
     Argument _q_ must be an element of [0,1].  To make use of this
     function, write first ‘load("distrib")’.


